The paper deals with software design patterns and their detection in source code, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for pattern detection, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of classical machine learning and deep learning approaches suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a new software representation technique, which could also fall under software development (cs.SD).
